('Terna College of Engineering', '60% of the students get placement. The average package is Rs. 3 lac p.a.The major companies are Infosys and Patni.Year 2008-09 2007-08 2006-07Maximum Salary: Rs. 3.3 lac p.a. Rs. 3.2 lac p.a. Rs. 5 lac p.a.Minimum Salary: Rs. 2.2 lac p.a. Rs. 1.44 lac p.a. Rs. 1.5 lac p.a. ', 'Anonymous'),
('Terna College of Engineering', 'its not a very bad college...this year almost 140 students got placed in TCS...others in ATOS,LnT ....wit satisfactory package.... ', 'Anonymous'),
('Terna College of Engineering', 'Terna Engineering College is just a 2-3 minute walk from Nerul Railway Station (Harbour Railway). Located in the campus is also the Medical College. ', 'Anonymous'),
