('Terna College of Engineering', 'Half the students are villagers. Boys to girls ratio is 6:4. All in all, an average crowd. ', 'Anonymous'),
('Terna College of Engineering', '80 % college crowd are villagers ', 'Anonymous'),
('Terna College of Engineering', 'Terna''s technical festival ‘AVALON’ takes place in September.Most of the events are robotic centered, and otherwise is quite dull. But the participants are quite zealous and show great efforts in making their ''mean-machines''.The cultural festival of Terna Engineering College ‘Resonance’ takes place in March. ', 'Anonymous'),
('Terna College of Engineering', 'Terna Engineering College is very strict regarding attendance. 75% is a must otherwise parents are called and given a sound lecture. If less then 40% students are detained. Seems like some kind of Bio-metric system has been installed for the attendance management of the students and the staff, so beware. ', 'Anonymous'),
('Terna College of Engineering', 'attendance is must be arouand 75% ', 'Anonymous'),
('Terna College of Engineering', 'Geeks may like this college as their lookout is not enjoyment. However, being engineers we can survive anything, isn''t it? A good bet for an average scorer in Navi Mumbai. ', 'Anonymous'),
